text: visionOS is a mixed reality operating system developed by Apple Inc. It is based on iPadOS, it was released on February 2, 2024 when Apple Vision Pro released. == Availability == visionOS was launched for the first time in United States, later, they were available on other countries when Apple Vision Pro came out. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Apple software Category:2024 establishments in the United States
title: VisionOS
